<section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-background">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
      
      <!-- Text Description -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-secondary border-s-4 border-secondary ps-6" data-i18n="hawza.title">What is Hawza?</h2>
        
        <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed" data-i18n="hawza.desc">
          The Hawza is more than an institution; it is a thousand-year-old ecosystem of learning. Unlike modern fragmented education, the Hawza system integrates <strong>rational sciences</strong> with <strong>spiritual purification</strong>.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary mt-1">history_edu</span>
            <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
              <strong data-i18n="hawza.socratic.title">The Socratic Method:</strong> <span data-i18n="hawza.socratic.desc">A unique tradition of debate (mubahatha) where students master texts through peer discussion.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary mt-1">psychology</span>
            <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
              <strong data-i18n="hawza.intellectual.title">Intellectual Depth:</strong> <span data-i18n="hawza.intellectual.desc">Moving beyond rote memorization to the mastery of Logic, Jurisprudence, and Metaphysics.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary mt-1">self_improvement</span>
            <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
              <strong data-i18n="hawza.adab.title">Cultivation of 'Adab':</strong> <span data-i18n="hawza.adab.desc">The development of character and spiritual etiquette as the foundation of all scholarship.</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Image/Diagram Container -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-secondary/5 -m-6 rounded-xl"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-white p-8 border border-outline/10 shadow-sm">
          <img 
            class="w-full aspect-square object-contain" 
            data-i18n-alt="hawza.diagram.alt"
            alt="A minimalist diagram representing the hierarchy of Islamic sciences from Language, Logic, Law, Theology to Philosophy." 
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAeJ7U20x5kWzg4-dKuDXC417AFcne5qKhPx8dxdcWZUDqbuJpaSSLSdF1c1usRryXk7N82Rsex1B6U_n3_2NKPLBVSyDVqCsj0HX7BDbWPfJzEWrSLTK--Gq8uduEJ-w8sS3DFK61HwaHsVO8DgIOIogl8BSrpRV7ksUz-7qTg8JHrbB2BlxCRdlH2AfYZe98yrfQz98XmbWyplq1wiLv7YUGJaXrTAKQJFHEUBnMQ_UwJhjOSkKtH"
          />
          <div class="mt-8 text-center">
            <p class="font-label-md text-label-md text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest" data-i18n="hawza.ascent">The Ascent of the Mind</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
